4. Compare posterior trees with true tree
========================================================

```{r eval=FALSE}
plot_densitree(
  c(true_tree, trees[[1]]),
  alpha = 1.0,
  scaleX = TRUE,
  width = c(6, 4),
  cex = 2,
  col = c("black", "red")
)
```
***
```{r echo=FALSE}
plot_densitree(
  c(true_tree, trees[[1]]),
  alpha = 1.0,
  scaleX = TRUE,
  width = c(6, 4),
  cex = 2,
  col = c("black", "red")
)
```

4. Compare posterior trees with true tree
========================================================

```{r eval=FALSE}
nltt_plot(true_tree)
nltt_lines(trees[[1]], col = "red")
```

 * nLTT statistic: area between the lines

*Janzen et al., 2015*

***
```{r echo=FALSE}
nltt_plot(true_tree, lwd = 6)
nltt_lines(trees[[1]], col = "red", lwd = 4)
```


4. Compare posterior trees with true tree
========================================================

```{r}
nltts <- nLTT::nltts_diff(true_tree, trees)
```

```{r eval=FALSE}
ggplot(
  data = data.frame(error = nltts),
  aes(x = error)
) + geom_histogram()
```
***
```{r echo=FALSE}
ggplot(
  data = data.frame(error = nltts),
  aes(x = error)
) + geom_histogram()
```

